x4freetext: Stacks of Am and U targets.
Data were compiled at the  Russia  MSU SINP  CDFE  by
and 243Am in energy  region  of  6  -  12  MeV  were
measured  at  the bremsstrahlung beams of the SSC RF
IPPE microtron with energy step from 59 to 200  keV.
The  measurements  were performed by relative method
by using of the photofission cross section  of  238U
The photofission cross sections  of  242Am-m  in  the
energy  region  of  6  -  12 MeV and of 243Am in the
ebergy region of 6 - 7 MeV were measured at first.
